code: @Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     int size = in.readVInt().     roles = new RoleDescriptor[size].     for (int i = 0. i < size. i++) {         roles[i] = new RoleDescriptor(in).     } }

@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeVInt(roles.length).     for (RoleDescriptor role : roles) {         role.writeTo(out).     } }
